item.title: Were do , and what do, I TRAIN!
item.dc:creator: @pk3r_l3g3nd pk3r l3g3nd
item.description:
@pk3r_l3g3nd wrote:

[quote=“scipyo, post:3, topic:360307”]Alright if you beat monkey madness the gaurds there are great exp I got 99 attack there
Also whip is def worth it.[/quote]

Yup, the monkey guards are great xp, very fast leveling and they heal on low hp which makes it even more xp per kill. Also bandits are awsome way, i get abt 60/75k per hour there and if you have saradomin or zammy equipment they auto attack you which is great with guthans. Another way is the lv 50 giant spiders , 3rd floor in stronghold of security. Also auto attack for short while,once they stop attacking you then just leave room and attack different monster then go back and they auto attack you again.

Good luck

item.title: Were do , and what do, I TRAIN!
item.dc:creator: @primadude Primadude
item.description:
@primadude wrote:

If you want to bot, bot on the moss giants in the chaos tunnels; there’s normally hardly anyone there and it’s good exp, since they have a low defence and a medium hp level. If you aren’t botting, I’d kill Cyclops’ - I can get around 60k exp/hour on them, and Im 107 combat, so you should be able to get a decent 30-40k/hour ;).
